	6029 120th Ave SE\n\nDescription\n\nThe City of Bellevue's Keep Bellevue B
	eautiful program is launching\n\n26 in '26\,\n\nan effort aimed at complet
	ing\n\n26 Signature Street cleanups\n\nin 2026. The goal is simple: show u
	p consistently\, take care of our streets and support cleaner\, more welco
	ming neighborhoods.\n\nUpcoming Cleanup - Newport\n\nDate:\n\nSaturday\, A
	pril 4\n\nTime:\n\n9-11 a.m.\n\nLocation:\n\nNewport neighborhood\n\nExper
	ience is not required\, and cleanup supplies will be provided. Come for th
	e full two hours or drop in and stay as long as you can. Coffee and water 
