	y 3\, 2026 at The Bush School\, Seattle. Early bird pricin g ends on March
	 1. Learn more about 3xBA and register at: https://www.3xba.com/register\n
	\nLink: https://3xba.ludus.com/index.php?show\\_id=200517791\n\nHelp your 
	athlete grow their game this spring with the 3xBA Spring 3x3 Clinic Series
	-a 5-week program combining fun\, competit ive 3x3 basketball with small-g
