DTSTAMP:20260401T023629Z
DTSTART:20260405T180000Z
DESCRIPTION:Issaquah Commons\, an open-air lifestyle center in Issaquah\, W
	ashington\, \\(https://www.issaquahcommons.com\\)\, invites the community 
	to celebrate the season as the Easter Bunny hops throughout the center on 
	Sunday\, April 5th\, from 11 a.m. to 3 p.m.\, offering guests the opportun
	ity to snap festive selfies\, enjoy special giveaways and take home sweet 
	treats. Families and visitors are encouraged to stroll the property\, keep
	 an eye out for the Easter Bunny’s appearances and join in the fun as he m
	akes his way around the center spreading springtime cheer. This event is f
	ree of charge and open to the public\; no pre-registration is required to 
	attend. For more information\, click here or visit https://issaquahcommons
	.com/events.\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/issaquah-com
	mons-welcomes-the-easter-bunny-for-a-one-day-visit/18408173/2026-04-05T00\
	n\nFrom SEAtoday - All Events
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/issaquah-commons-welcomes
	-the-easter-bunny-for-a-one-day-visit/18408173/2026-04-05T00
LOCATION:Issaquah Commons\, 705-975 NW Gilman Blvd\, Issaquah\, WA
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:seatoday-all
CATEGORIES:SEAtoday - All Events
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT4H
