UID:ADiIEeoGhbTDp3il3vwop
SUMMARY:The Garden w/ Ghost Mountain
DTSTAMP:20260401T023629Z
DTSTART:20260407T020000Z
DESCRIPTION:THE GARDEN IS A CONSTANTLY EVOLVING BAND ORIGINALLY FROM ORANGE
	 COUNTY\, CALIFORNIA. ESTABLISHED IN 2011 BY WYATT AND FLETCHER SHEARS. TH
	EY HAVE BEEN TOURING SINCE 2012 AND HAVE PLAYED IN DIFFERENT REGIONS INCLU
	DING THE UNITED KINGDOM\, EUROPE\, UNITED STATES\, ASIA\, AUSTRALIA\, MEXI
	CO & CANADA\, THEY CREATED THE TERM\, "VADA VADA" IN 2011 TO REPRESENT THE
	IR MUSIC AND OTHER CREATIONS. VADA VADA IS A TERM THAT REPRESENTS TOTAL FR
	EEDOM OF EXPRESSION WITHOUT BOUNDARIES OR GUIDELINES OF ANY SORT. THEY HAV
	E BECOME KNOWN FOR THEIR ENERGETIC AND OFF THE WALL PERFORMANCES AROUND TH
	E WORLD\, AND ARE PROLIFICALLY TOURING\, RELEASING MUSIC AND OTHER CONTENT
	.\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/the-garden-w-ghost-moun
	tain/18151703/2026-04-06T00\n\nFrom SEAtoday - All Events
